flowchart TD
    Input[Input batch]
    GT["Ground-truth hard labels<br/>(one-hot)"]
    Teacher["Teacher model<br/>BERT-base (frozen, large)"]
    Student["Student model<br/>DistilBERT or T5-small (trainable)"]

    T_logits["Teacher logits"]
    S_logits["Student logits"]
    T_soft["Softmax(logits / T)<br/>Soft labels (teacher)"]
    S_soft["Softmax(logits / T)<br/>Soft labels (student)"]
    S_hard["Softmax(logits)<br/>Student predictions"]

    CE["Cross-Entropy loss<br/>(hard target)"]
    KL["KL Divergence loss<br/>(soft target)"]
    Loss["Total loss =<br/>alpha * CE + (1 - alpha) * KL"]

    Note1["T=1: hard distribution<br/>T=4: smooth, richer signal<br/>alpha=0.5 typical"]

    Input --> Teacher --> T_logits --> T_soft
    Input --> Student
    Student --> S_logits --> S_soft
    Student --> S_hard
    GT --> CE
    S_hard --> CE
    T_soft --> KL
    S_soft --> KL
    CE --> Loss
    KL --> Loss
    Teacher -. knowledge transfer .-> Student
    Loss --- Note1
